# franz-go pkg/kgo tests known to pass against tansu (run by run.sh).
#
# FINDINGS.md records the compatibility gaps behind the tests that are
# excluded: TestClient_ProduceLargeMessages (max.message.bytes not
# enforced), TestGroupETL (UNKNOWN_MEMBER_ID under concurrent
# rebalances), TestTxnEtl (aborted records visible to read_committed).
#
# TestSCRAMAuth/TestSCRAMAuthBadCredentials self-skip without
# KGO_TEST_SCRAM; TestShareGroup*/Test*848* self-skip because tansu does
# not advertise ShareFetch v2 / ConsumerGroupHeartbeat v1.

